import React from 'react';
import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom'
import AppBar from '@material-ui/core/AppBar';
import Toolbar from '@material-ui/core/Toolbar'
import TypoGraphy from '@material-ui/core/Typography'
import { Home } from '@material-ui/icons'

const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <AppBar position="static" color="default" >
            <Toolbar>
                <TypoGraphy>

                        <NavLink  style={{ textDecoration: "none"}} exact activeStyle={{ color: 'blue'}} to='/'>
                            Home 
                        </NavLink> |
                        
                        <NavLink style={{ textDecoration: "none"}} exact activeStyle={{ color: 'blue'}} to='/posts'>
                            Postings
                        </NavLink> |  

                        <NavLink style={{ textDecoration: "none"}} exact activeStyle={{ color: 'blue'}} to='/users/login'>
                            Login
                        </NavLink> |  

                        <NavLink style={{ textDecoration: "none"}} exact activeStyle={{ color: 'blue'}} to='/users/signup'>
                            Register
                        </NavLink> | 

                </TypoGraphy>
            </Toolbar> 
        </AppBar>
        </>
    );
};

export default Navbar;
